{"tid":816608,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"泰利為家庭放棄加盟斯巴達","createTime":"2018-09-13T00:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T07:03:33.000Z","uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"265d16249d7b7a6fd69e054ae13354dbce0561f6","tid":816608,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T00:49:10.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=qrZihtvkcViWUrD%2FnB6oPfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=f4326420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】上周已通過體測、預備加盟俄超莫斯科斯巴達的泰利，突然宣佈因家庭理由交易告吹。<br />\n<br />\n「斯巴達是一支雄心萬丈的球隊，我對該會的專業精神十分敬佩。不過，跟家人商議之後，我們認為加盟斯巴達並非目前最好的選擇。」37歲的泰利（John Terry）在instagram上說。<br />\n<br />\n斯巴達準備向泰利提供一紙1年300萬鎊的合約，另有1年續約條款，以為萬事俱備，豈料觸礁收場。<br />\n<br />\n「我要借這個機會感謝斯巴達的一番盛情，亦祝願斯巴達與斯巴達球迷在餘下球季取得成功。」前英格蘭隊長泰利續說。<br />\n<br />\n在車仔度過19個寒暑之後，上季泰利改投英冠的阿士東維拉，在各項賽事上陣36場射入1球，但在升班附加賽決賽維拉以0:1不敵富咸，而泰利季後亦宣佈離隊，據報是因為維拉付不起他高昂的周薪。"},{"pid":"71c84def68c6550a14419b07a3701c0c0b53987f","tid":816608,"uid":19126,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T01:03:03.000Z","msg":"太多俄妹，屋企人唔贊成了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0b089fa746699e7ca4cd5bdd39bf5600c32912","tid":816608,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T01:20:24.000Z","msg":"今次又睇中邊個嘅老婆所以留低？"},{"pid":"0c887147045a765d397a559266fa6dab47366a62","tid":816608,"uid":33789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T01:22:25.000Z","msg":"普京老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec5781523784a0c772e238dae4c5207dad15c87","tid":816608,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T01:26:26.000Z","msg":"去剷雪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1eaad4b03784cc85bab9aa1db04d538022badf","tid":816608,"uid":734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T01:34:32.000Z",